Automatic Downloader is a simple python script that lets you download things quickly off a webpage. 
The adventage to using it over using something like wget on unix is that unlike wget it downloads files 
in parallel. You can specify the maximum number of concurrent downloads.

Usage:
python downloader.py www.example.com
python downloader.py www.example.com -d path/to/dest

Options:
downloader <url> [options]
            Options are:
            -t (--threads): number of threads to use when downloading files
            -d (--dst): destination where the donwloaded files will be saved to

